title: GlenOak backs 'don't run soft,' a big reason the Golden Eagles are leading Federal League
text: GlenOak backs 'don’t run soft,' a big reason the Golden Eagles are leading Federal League GlenOak has used a bevy of backs to seize first place in the Federal League. They come in different shapes and sizes, but they share one quality: They’re not afraid to be physical.
